{
  "stem": "24814.2",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we had the nice experience of rolling into a liberated city with people screaming and yelling and waving and handing flowers and bottles of wine through the windows, and so on.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And it was a savage fight for a while, because again, it was Heinrich Himmler-- prestige area, with his SS troops.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They were fighting the 10th SS Mountain Division.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we met the French-- Algerian division coming up from the Swiss border, and that was it.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "The last French soil was cleared.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But I had an interesting experience.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I wrote it in my book.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because I speak German, I was involved in picking up the leading Nazi collaborator in lower Alsace.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Do you have time to talk about it?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Absolutely.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "What was his name?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Ulmar, as I recall.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] We-- after the fighting stopped, we set up our command post in a Gasthaus, an inn.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we looked around for the owner-- usually, you made a deal for the occupation forces, you'll be paid for your this, the yadda-- is it all right?",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because this is France, after all.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Nobody around.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And about evening, a little Alsatian peasant came up.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was talking to the guard and the intelligence officer, who didn't speak a word of either French or German.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I went out and talked to him, and he said, do you want to pick up the biggest Nazi collaborator in all Alsace?",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I said, certainly we do.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He said, he's the Burgermeister of this town.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's his inn you're in that you took over.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we all picked up Tommy guns and got two Jeeps, and we got the little farm-- the little farmer was so afraid of this man, he didn't want to go with us.",
      "word_count": 33
    }
  ],
